      "content": "idk i just dont want to pay for a specialist if i dont have to. its just a bit of redness and grit. the drops aren't even expired, they just opened a few months ago. if i just use the drops and maybe some warm compresses, wouldn't that be enough to soothe it if it's just strain? i dont think it's a big deal.",
