    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "but i literally checked the bottle and it says it's good for 6 months after opening. i'm pretty sure it's fine. i really dont have the time to go to a clinic right now. if i just take an ibuprofen for the pain and use the drops like i said, is there really any reason that would be dangerous? like, what's the worst that happens if it's just dry eyes?",
